{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775859906209,"sessionID":"ses_286807052ffemi6XSXwi2xYdi4","part":{"id":"prt_d797fb147001jwn7wfxkoVhCsP","messageID":"msg_d797fa9ac001QokQJQLMFx2BRY","sessionID":"ses_286807052ffemi6XSXwi2xYdi4","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_7e4110d66fd4465facfb173d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md","limit":20},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-019 — CLI Binary Entry Points (4 Binaries) Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** cmd  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** M  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Implementation Tasks\n11: \n12: ### Phase 1: Verify/Complete agentd (cmd/agentd/main.go)\n13: \n14: - [ ] **T001** Verify `cmd/agentd/main.go` - confirm it compiles and matches design:\n15:   - Uses controller-runtime manager\n16:   - Watches Sandbox CRD\n17:   - Imports `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd` reconciler\n18:   - Metrics disabled (`BindAddress: \"0\"`)\n19:   - Health probe disabled\n20: \n\n(Showing lines 1-20 of 215. Use offset=21 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-019 — CLI Binary Entry Points (4 Binaries) Tasks\n\n**Module:** cmd  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Verify/Complete agentd (cmd/agentd/main.go)\n\n- [ ] **T001** Verify `cmd/agentd/main.go` - confirm it compiles and matches design:\n  - Uses controller-runtime manager\n  - Watches Sandbox CRD\n  - Imports `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd` reconciler\n  - Metrics disabled (`BindAddress: \"0\"`)\n  - Health probe disabled\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410